name: The magnificent starburst galaxy Messier 82
description:
This mosaic image of the magnificent starburst galaxy, Messier 82 (M82) is the sharpest wide-angle view ever obtained of M82. 

Name:	Cigar Galaxy, Messier 82
Type:	Local Universe : Galaxy : Activity : Starburst
Distance:	13 million light years
Constellation:	Ursa Major
Category:	Anniversary Galaxies
